{"tid":1950851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃文廸將婚宴延後4個月至7月19日","createTime":"2020-03-30T14:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T06:41:44.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6cae2fe8904a2679dded491bbd973d0852e2a5","tid":1950851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"昨為婚嫁大好日，原本訂了18圍酒席的新人黃文廸（後右）及廖皓晴（後左）因應政府推出限聚令，將婚宴席數減了又減，最後仍無法與證婚同日舉行婚宴，延遲4個月才舉行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200330/s00006/8bc2f09eea6a7aacf7c912cc946b42fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200330%2Fs00006%2F8bc2f09eea6a7aacf7c912cc946b42fe.jpg&h=c48a6ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年3月30日<br />\n婚禮限20人 新人「吉場」證婚<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200330/s00001/1585507003950/%e5%a9%9a%e7%a6%ae%e9%99%9020%e4%ba%ba-%e6%96%b0%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%8c%e5%90%89%e5%a0%b4%e3%80%8d%e8%ad%89%e5%a9%9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200330%2Fs00001%2F1585507003950%2F%25e5%25a9%259a%25e7%25a6%25ae%25e9%2599%259020%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e6%2596%25b0%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2590%2589%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%25a9%259a&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2W0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=3a74b617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200330%2Fs00001%2F1585507003950%2F%25e5%25a9%259a%25e7%25a6%25ae%25e9%2599%259020%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e6%2596%25b0%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2590%2589%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%25a9%259a&h=9afd5d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200330/s00001/1585507003950/%e5%a9%9a%e7%a6%ae%e9%99%9020%e4%ba%ba-%e6%96%b0%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%8c%e5%90%89%e5%a0%b4%e3%80%8d%e8%ad%89%e5%a9%9a</a><br />\n【明報專訊】偌大的廳堂，禮台上的佈置寫着「Pinky &amp; Tik」，3月29日，是庚子年結婚吉日。一對新人徐徐步入廳堂，不過，迎面等待着他們的卻是18席空桌，沒有掌聲、沒有歡呼聲。「限聚令」下，婚禮不容多於20人，「原本今日（昨日）舉行證婚連飲宴，如所有都取消，我就覺得這兩年的籌備，什麼都沒有了。」新娘子哭訴，可幸酒樓最終開放場地證婚，在12名親友的見證下，二人笑着踏入人生新階段。<br />\n<br />\n政府日前宣布，因疫情禁止人群聚集，新人黃文廸及廖皓晴最初得悉，婚宴場地須按一般食肆的要求4人一枱，立刻由18圍減至11圍，但其後得知婚禮儀式上只容許不多於20人出席，令二人大失預算︰「一場婚禮怎止20人？律師、攝影師、雙方父母已經8人，兄弟姊妹再多幾個也不行。我們沒有想過會這樣，真的好大打擊。」新娘廖皓晴說。<br />\n<br />\n新郎黃文廸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />表示，他們兩年前開始籌備婚禮，所有儀式跟足傳統習俗，「擇吉日、擇吉時都有做，如果連證婚都舉行不了，怕不吉利」<span style=\"color: red;\">。最後，二人與酒樓商量好，只在場地如期舉行證婚，而婚宴則延後4個月至7月19日</span>，「我們都明白疫情嚴重，有限制不緊要，但可否早一日宣布，整場婚禮變得混亂，我們很無奈」。<br />\n<br />\n業界：上半年婚禮全改期<br />\n部分無限期延遲<br />\n負責是次婚禮統籌的Jessica認為，因應疫情發展，一直與新人跟進，惟政府宣布政策含糊不清，「為何政府不將重要的事一次過說清楚？不然就一刀切禁止晚市，新人就不用惶恐，只能選擇改期」。她又說，她手上於上半年舉行的婚禮已全部改期，部分更無限期延遲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200330/s00006/8bc2fa17bd02adaa550b75d6c329da90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200330%2Fs00006%2F8bc2fa17bd02adaa550b75d6c329da90.jpg&h=310c769f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府因應疫情禁止人群聚集，婚禮只容20人出席。昨日一場證婚儀式上，一對新人、新人父母、協助婚禮的8名兄弟姊妹、3名攝影師、1名律師、1名婚禮統籌，共19人，剛好合符規限。不過因在場有記者，一度多於20人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef038e26a03f4e0f599b010caae75220f5d20c7","tid":1950851,"uid":6003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:55:27.000Z","msg":"4個月乜事都可以發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ef4fb39ecf21acfc610e62b223d951c4aa2ef4","tid":1950851,"uid":75028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"真係嗰個黃文迪？"},{"pid":"72927648ec8998a7c36c4fd1f23242a5b66c28d8","tid":1950851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"文廸就是垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9xaS74b8yH78UuAl0V/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9xaS74b8yH78UuAl0V%2Fgiphy.gif&h=125ca831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/9-03-2018/QlFKSF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-03-2018%2FQlFKSF.gif&h=53e3b6eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc6cd7f270b760d3a0ca659dcaa62bca45dfecd0","tid":1950851,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"你估四個月後就搞得掂？你睇下一月到四月，似到頂喇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75426447e44edb4d776e1486f0afc420b22c70ab","tid":1950851,"uid":166655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"昨日一場證婚儀式上，一對新人、新人父母、協助婚禮的8名兄弟姊妹、3名攝影師、1名律師、1名婚禮統籌，共19人，剛好合符規限。不過因在場有記者，一度多於20人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又好似係一條搵食橋<br />\n結婚公司搵一班人去做嘢，搞到多過20人，叫主辦單位俾錢走，又賺一筆"},{"pid":"874fe68748a7260ec7f32e78bda01edae975bdea","tid":1950851,"uid":3086,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"我以為係射盲印尼女記者嗰隻仆街..."},{"pid":"9a2885382c07acc10becce075844b0eb73f1a67c","tid":1950851,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec5a3fe85956692281322e7339e758a4c422c88","tid":1950851,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"唔係呀Dick <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94016d73f60edb95e74d3a259f159f47bf7d1b76","tid":1950851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874fe68748a7260ec7f32e78bda01edae975bdea","tid":1950851,"uid":3086,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"